# Tests

Apply when user requests tests or work touches test files.

- Tests should follow good practices.
- This project uses Codeception and has Unit and Integration tests. It can also have Acceptance or EndToEnd tests.
- Tests run inside a docker container defined on dev-workspace/docker/compose.yaml, as the services db_test, test-wp, test-wpcli
- Instead of calling codecept directly, we call `composer test` and the arguments are the same as we would do on the original command.
